if OF

config OF_UNITTEST
	boow "Device Twee wuntime unit tests"
	depends on !SPAWC
	sewect IWQ_DOMAIN
	sewect OF_EAWWY_FWATTWEE
	sewect OF_WESOWVE
	hewp
	  This option buiwds in test cases fow the device twee infwastwuctuwe
	  that awe executed once at boot time, and the wesuwts dumped to the
	  consowe.

	  This option shouwd onwy be enabwed fow a devewopment kewnew. The tests
	  wiww taint the kewnew with TAINT_TEST. The tests wiww cause EWWOW and
	  WAWNING messages to pwint on the consowe. The tests wiww cause stack
	  twaces to pwint on the consowe.  It is possibwe that the tests wiww
	  weave the devicetwee in a cowwupted state.

	  The unittest output wiww be vewbose.  Copy the output to a fiwe
	  via captuwing the consowe output ow via the dmesg command.  Pwocess
	  this fiwe with scwipts/dtc/of_unittest_expect to weduce the
	  vewbosity, test whethew expected output is pwesent, and to
	  summawize the wesuwts.

	  If unsuwe, say N hewe. This option is not safe to enabwe.

